description:
AWS Service Catalog  AWS Service Catalog [https://aws.amazon.com/servicecatalog/] enables
organizations to create and manage catalogs of IT services that are approved for
use on AWS. To get the most out of this documentation, you should be familiar
with the terminology discussed in AWS Service Catalog Concepts
[http://docs.aws.amazon.com/servicecatalog/latest/adminguide/what-is_concepts.html]
